title: The Start of Big 12 Media Days
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, Dusty Dvoracek, & Andre Ware break down Baylor, Oklahoma State, Kansas, West Virginia, & Kansas State. Mike Gundy takes the podium. Kansas State standout Deuce Vaughn also gives an interview.
